text: Herbert Frankenhauser (July 23, 1945 - May 6, 2020) was a German politician. He was a member of the Christian Social Union of Bavaria. He was a member of the Bundestag from 1990 to 2013. Frankenhauser was born in Munich. Frankenhauser died on May 6, 2020 at the age of 74.Herbert Frankenhauser ==References== Category:1945 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Politicians from Munich
